Hollyoaks actress Jorgie Porter, 34, debuted her baby bump at the British Soap Awards 2022 on Saturday evening, just days after announcing her pregnancy. The blonde beauty looked the epitome of glamour in a strapless white gown which clung to her growing belly.She beamed on the red carpet with her hair styled in a sleek bun which was paired with subtle eye makeup and a nude lip.Jorgie announced her pregnancy earlier this week.She shared a bittersweet post on TikTok of her scan picture with the caption: “Hopeful beginnings.”In November Jorgie and her fiance Ollie Piotrowski miscarried quadruplets at 14 weeks.